Package basic_mitre.cvss

Class CVSS2object

  • java.lang.Object
    • basic_mitre.cvss.CVSS2object
  • @Entity(name="cvss2")
public class CVSS2object
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a CVSS v2 object (Base score metrics, ...)

    It can create a CVSS v2 (base metric v2) object from given parameters and return it Objects can be put into database including quick updates

    Author:
    Tomas Bozek (XarfNao)
